<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Php on Sidnei Weber</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/tags/php/</link><description>Recent content in Php on Sidnei Weber</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>pt-br</language><copyright>© 2025 Sidnei Weber</copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Oct 2016 14:34:10 -0300</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://sidneiweber.com.br/tags/php/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Remover extensão .php com .htaccess (Rápido e fácil)</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/remover-extensao-php-com-htaccess-rapido-e-facil/</link><pubDate>Mon, 17 Oct 2016 14:34:10 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/remover-extensao-php-com-htaccess-rapido-e-facil/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Já havia tentado de várias maneiras remover a extensão .php dos meus arquivos, mas todas sem sucesso. Porém consegui fazer de uma maneira muito simples, editando o arquivo .htaccess. Lembrando que para funcionar a modulo &amp;ldquo;mod_rewrite&amp;rdquo; deve estar habilitado no seu servidor web.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Utilizando o comando like com variável [PHP-MySQL]</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/utilizando-o-comando-like-com-variavel-php-mysql/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2015 16:48:54 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/utilizando-o-comando-like-com-variavel-php-mysql/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;conexao.php&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$busca&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$_POST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;busca&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;];&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// comando like com variavel
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// retorna todos os produtos que tenham o valor da variável busca em qualquer posição
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;mysql_query&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;SELECT descricao FROM produtos WHERE descricao like &amp;#39;%&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$busca&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;%&amp;#39; &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// comando like normal
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;//retorna todos os nomes que tenham a palavra &amp;#34;pedro&amp;#34; em qualquer posição
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;mysql_query&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34; SELECT nome FROM funcionarios WHERE nome like &amp;#39;%pedro%&amp;#39; &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;pre&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Maiúsculas e Minúsculas em PHP</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/maiusculas-e-minusculas-em-php/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2015 15:47:02 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/maiusculas-e-minusculas-em-php/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;$texto =&amp;ldquo;warquia pereira santos&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;vamos transformar a variavel $texto&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;=&amp;gt; Converte a string para letras minúsculas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;strtolower();&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;srttolower&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$texto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;vai sair assim = warquia pereira santos&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;=&amp;gt; Converte a string para letras maiúsculas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
strtoupper();&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Configurar PHP para exibir erros</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/configurar-php-para-exibir-erros/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2015 15:40:25 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/configurar-php-para-exibir-erros/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Essa configuração útil quando estamos desenvolvendo e precisamos ver alguns erros gerados pelo nosso código. Basta editar o arquivo &lt;strong&gt;php.ini&lt;/strong&gt; que no Linux geralmente fica em &lt;strong&gt;/etc/php5/apache2/php.ini&lt;/strong&gt; e trocar a configuração da chave:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Melhor maneira de converter data para mysql [PHP]</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/melhor-maneira-de-converter-data-para-mysql-php/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2013 14:08:08 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/posts/melhor-maneira-de-converter-data-para-mysql-php/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Se você quer converter uma data vinda do MYSQL para o formato PT-BR use o seguinte comando:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$data&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;implode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;/&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;array_reverse&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;explode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;-&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Assim vai converter a data do mysql para o formato brasileiro.&lt;/p&gt;
